title: Episode 14 - Lil Yachty
description:
Lil Yachty joins for a chaotic interview about pizza, Bryce Hall, and opening packages. Josh and Dave break down what's actually going down at The Sway House, and Brianna says maybe the most shocking thing we've heard on this show during Zoomer vs Boomer.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
